trans-unit.source: What not to expect\n
trans-unit.target: 不应发生\n

trans-unit.resname:
•	Any prescription for narcotics or DEA (Drug Enforcement Administration) controlled substances (Schedule I, II, III, IV)
•	Any prescriptions for medications that are restricted by individual states
•	Any prescriptions for psychiatric or lifestyle medications (for example, diet or erectile dysfunction drugs)
•	Consults in languages other than English
•	Instant responses to inbox / message consults (consider video consults with available doctors for faster care)
trans-unit.source:
•	Any prescription for narcotics or DEA (Drug Enforcement Administration) controlled substances (Schedule I, II, III, IV)
•	Any prescriptions for medications that are restricted by individual states
•	Any prescriptions for psychiatric or lifestyle medications (for example, diet or erectile dysfunction drugs)
•	Consults in languages other than English
•	Instant responses to inbox / message consults (consider video consults with available doctors for faster care)
trans-unit.target:
•	麻醉品或DEA（禁毒执法管理）受控物质（附表I, II, III, IV）
•	所有受个别国家限制的药物处方
•	所有精神病学或生活方式药物处方（例如，饮食或勃起功能障碍药物）
•	用英语以外的其它语言咨询
•	即时回复收件箱/消息咨询（考虑与空闲医生的视频咨询，以获得更快的医护）
